62">“七国军”</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-lady-gaga-join-andy-samberg-for-surprise-dick-in-a-box-duet-on-snl50-3838327">Lady Gaga与安迪·桑伯格（Andy Samberg）合作，获得了寂寞岛的惊喜混合泳</a>。</p><p>在周年纪念剧集本身中，过去和现在的超级巨星<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/paul-simon">保罗·西蒙（Paul Simon）</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/sabrina-carpenter">萨布丽娜·卡彭特（Sabrina Carpenter）</a>唱了<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/sabrina-carpenter-and-paul-simon-perform-homeward-bound-on-snl50-anniversary-episode-3838559">《家》</a> ，<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/paul-mccartney">保罗·麦卡特尼（Paul McCartney）</a>在该节目中出现了第五次演出，表演了<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-beatles">甲壳虫乐队</a>“ Abbey Road”中的<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-paul-mccartneys-abbey-road-medley-for-snl50-anniversary-special-3838544">歌曲</a>。</p><p>同时，一名妇女<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/jay-z-and-diddy-sexual-assault-lawsuit-dropped-3838276">声称她在2000年被Jay-Z和Sean“ Diddy” Combs 13岁时受到性侵犯，最近自愿撤回了诉讼</a>。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/former-saturday-night-live-writer-recalls-jay-z-asking-to-swap-prop-joint-for-real-one-during-will-ferrell-sketch-3838704">前“周六夜现场”作家帖子回忆起杰伊·Z（Jay-Z）要求将道具联合交换为皇家（Will Ferrell）在Will Ferrell Sketch期间</a>首次出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
