div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center; margin-bottom: 24px;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 224px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 144px;"></div></div><p></p><p style=" color:#c9c8cd; font-family:Arial,sans-serif; font-size:14px; line-height:17px; margin-bottom:0; margin-top:8px; overflow:hidden; padding:8px 0 7px; text-align:center; text-overflow:ellipsis; white-space:nowrap;"> <a href="https://www.instagram.com/reel/DFu3ZyBzEea/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" style=" color:#c9c8cd; font-family:Arial,sans-serif; font-size:14px; font-style:normal; font-weight:normal; line-height:17px; text-decoration:none;" target="_blank">NME（@nmemagazine）共享的帖子</a></p></div></blockquote><p><script async src="//platform.instagram.com/en_US/embeds.js"></script></p><p>奥兹（Ozzy）的妻子和经理讨论了星光熠熠的阵容，并评论说：“您能想象所有这些家伙的照片结束时的照片吗？这里有一大堆图标。那张结局的照片将是不可思议的，历史上将倒下。”</p><p>尽管已经确认了奥兹·奥斯本（Ozzy Osbourne）在黑安息日（Black Sabbath）的表现，但鉴于他的健康状况，他的参与程度受到质疑。 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/ozzy-osbourne-only-playing-little-bits-and-pieces-with-black-sabbath-at-final-reunion-gig-3838506">然而，现在，传奇的主唱和黑暗王子已经开启了七月的黑人安息日在舞台上可以期望他在舞台上有多少球迷开放</a>。</p><p>他说，在他在<em>Siriusxm</em>上的Ozzy演讲节目的最新演讲中即将举行的演出时说：“我不打算与Black Sabbath一起做一场演出，但我正在和他们一起做一些小零碎的东西。我正在尽我所能，感到舒适。”</p><p>奥斯本（Osbourne）最后一次在2018年进行了全套演出，他补充说：“我想重新站起来。当您早上起床时，您就跳下床。我必须平衡自己，但我还没有死。我仍在积极做事。”</p><p>此更新是在<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/ozzy-osbourne-says-he-cant-walk-ahead-of-black-sabbaths-final-show-sharon-says-illness-doesnt-affect-his-voice-3835987">Ozzy透露，他现在由于帕金森氏病而“无法走路”</a> 。但是，他的妻子和经理沙龙向粉丝们保证，他的病“不会影响他的声音”。帕金森氏症是一种进步疾病。这不是您可以稳定的东西。它会影响身体的不同部位，并影响了他的腿。但是他的声音和以往一样好。”她解释说。</p><p>演唱会的门票上周五（2月14日）发售， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/fans-react-to-rush-for-black-sabbath-final-gig-tickets-3838021">许多球迷感到沮丧，试图确保门票</a>。有些人还批评了高<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/black-sabbaths-final-gig-in-birmingham-ticket-prices-revealed-3836924">票价</a>- 尽管所有利润都在帕金森氏菌，伯明翰儿童医院和橡子儿童临终关怀中平均分配。 Others though were delighted that they managed to get their hands on tickets for the show.</p><p> Meanwhile, Sabbath members <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/tony-iommi-shares-emotional-statement-on-final-black-sabbath-show-what-we-created-together-was-bigger-than-any-one-of-us-3835182">Iommi</a> and <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-geezer-butler-share-first-statement-on-black-sabbaths-final-gig-3835492">Butler</a> both recently shared statements about the upcoming reunion on social media. <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/classic-era-ozzy-osbourne-bassist-bob-daisley-speaks-out-on-being-snubbed-from-final-gig-it-could-be-an-embarrassment-but-well-see-3836634">Bob Daisley – the classic era Ozzy bassist – also talked about not being invited to perform at the band&#39;s last show</a> .</p><p> The post <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/guns-n-roses-tool-and-jason-momoa-lead-new-additions-to-all-star-line-up-for-ozzy-osbourne-and-black-sabbaths-final-gig-3838660">Guns &#39;N&#39; Roses, Tool and Jason Momoa lead new additions to all-star line-up for Ozzy Osbourne and Black Sabbath&#39;s final gig</a> appeared first on <a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a> .</p> ;
