ively-in-voice-note-im-going-to-fuck-up-im-going-to-say-the-wrong-thing-3832895">a six-minute voice note</a> from Baldoni to Lively was published, where he appeared to apologise to his co-star and say “I am far from perfect. I am a flawed man”. On January 31, <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/blake-lively-compares-herself-to-khaleesi-in-game-of-thrones-3833465">texts were submitted as part of Baldoni&#39;s filing</a> where Blake Lively compared herself to Khaleesi in Game Of Thrones, as well as calling <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/taylor-swift">Taylor Swift</a> and Ryan Reynolds her “dragons”.</p><p> The post <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/tv/ryan-reynolds-surprises-blake-lively-with-justin-baldoni-joke-at-snl50-3838636">Ryan Reynolds surprises Blake Lively with Justin Baldoni joke at &#39;SNL50&#39;</a> appeared first on <a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a> .</p> ;
